00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:18,560
乔布斯对控诉他偷了图形用户界面的反应
is Jobs' reaction to the claim that he stole the GUI.

223
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:20,560
他对此很冷静
He's pretty philosophical about it.

224
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:25,280
