He quotes Picasso, saying, "Good artists copy, great artists steal."

225
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:29,760
他告诉一位记者 “我们总是无耻地窃取伟大的创意 ”
He tells one reporter, "We have always been shameless about stealing great ideas."

226
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:32,800
伟大的艺术家偷窃 好吧
Great artists steal. Okay.

227
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:35,400
我的意思是 我们说的并不是严格意义上的“偷窃”
I mean, we're not talking about stealing in a hard sense.

228
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:37,680
没人拿到了专有的源代码
Nobody's obtaining proprietary source code

229
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:40,280
