他们给了我们非常重要的反馈
They gave us very important feedback,

240
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:29,520
总的来说 我认为我们的关系非常好
and in general I would say the relationship was pretty good.

241
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:34,120
但我也注意到 在我与技术主管的交谈中
But I also noticed in my conversations with the technical lead,

242
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:40,320
