and I got the idea that they were trying to copy the Macintosh.

244
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:47,560
我很早以前就向史蒂夫·乔布斯反馈过这件事
I told Steve Jobs about it pretty early on,

245
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:53,080
但在 1983 年秋天 这件事发展到了高潮
but it really came to a head in the fall of 1983.

246
