就在 1983 年 11 月的 COMDEX 上发布了 Windows
they announced Windows at the COMDEX in November 1983

248
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:04,000
对此史蒂夫·乔布斯勃然大怒
and Steve Jobs hit the roof.

249
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:06,400
他认为那是一种背叛
He really considered that a betrayal.

