威胁将会起诉任何看过 UNIX 源代码后又创建自己操作系统的人
they threatened lawsuits on anyone making their own OS after looking at UNIX source code.

322
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:21,040
这些人的占有欲简直是另一种层面
These guys were next - level proprietary.

323
