用这两家公司的话来说
All those programmers were,

324
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:26,800
所有这些程序员都在“精神上受到了污染”
in the words of the two companies, "mentally contaminated,"

325
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:29,160
因为他们都见过 UNIX 代码
because they'd seen UNIX code.

326
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:30,640
在 UNIX 系统实验室
In a famous court case

327
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:33,800
和伯克利软件设计公司之间的一个著名的法庭案例中
between UNIX System Laboratories and Berkeley Software Design,

328
00:19:33,800 --> 00:19:37,480
有人认为即使它本身没有使用 UNIX 代码
it was argued that any functionally similar system,

329
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:41,400
拥有类似功能的系统也侵犯版权
even though it didn't use the UNIX code itself, was a breach of copyright.

330
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:44,480
Paul Jones 当时是一名开发人员
Paul Jones was a developer at that time.

331
