他现在是数字图书馆 ibiblio.org 的主管 He's now the director of the digital library ibiblio.org.

332
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:56,360
他们的观点是 任何看过代码的人 都受到了精神污染
Anyone who has seen any of the code is mentally contaminated was their argument.

333
00:19:56,360 --> 00:20:03,040
