it's not enough just to give someone the improvement.

394
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:49,000
你必须和他们分享这些变化的所有细节代码
You actually have to share with them the nuts and bolts of all those changes.

395
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:52,120
然后这些改进足够好时 也许就会被 Linux 所吸收
Then they are adapted into Linux if they're good enough.

396
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:55,320
事实证明 这种公开的方式极具吸引力
That public approach proved massively attractive.

