and an advocate for free and open source software.

407
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:30,880
当开源软件第一次出现的时候 所有的操作系统都是专有的
When open source software first came out, the OS was all proprietary.

408
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:36,400
